{"tid":712534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"每日150單程證配額，唔係基本法或法律規定，絕對有得傾","createTime":"2018-06-22T07:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T08:20:13.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01f9aa73d5492dabc67e3030a0003f5051dacaea","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=30609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D30609&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=43dc218f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=30609</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1029611a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1029611a&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=844a48b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1029611a&h=5f5d170d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1029611a</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/137991/單程證-觀點-審批權只屬中方-先要正視中港出入境管理史\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F137991%2F%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89-%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E-%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9%E6%AC%8A%E5%8F%AA%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9-%E5%85%88%E8%A6%81%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8F%B2&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0c5fa34f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/137991/單程證-觀點-審批權只屬中方-先要正視中港出入境管理史</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180116/mobile/bkn-20180116190542769-0116_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180116%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180116190542769-0116_00822_001.html&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=54c51e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180116/mobile/bkn-20180116190542769-0116_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單程證、即「前往港澳通行證」每日150個配額原來「有得傾」。立法會議員譚文豪今日(16日)在人力事務委員會指出，<strong>《基本法》從沒有明文規定150個配額是硬性指標</strong>，質問當局<strong>為何不與內地檢討配額數目</strong>。政務司司長辦公室政策及項目統籌處處長關婉儀承認，港府可就配額數目與中央協商，惟單程證的目的是有序地讓內地配偶來港與家人團聚，現時中港跨境婚姻佔香港整體婚姻數量達30%，<strong>作為人道安排，有關配額量有需要維持</strong>。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每日150唔係無得傾，但弊在左膠和大愛膠當道。</span>"},{"pid":"32e2d9ee47c927b584f3279ed6e410ac2dabb547","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"首先積極鼓勵内地人到香港的反而是香港政府。<br />\n<br />\n2003年，香港政府發表《人口政策報告書》指出，香港生育率過低是長遠的挑戰，人口政策的首要目標是「讓香港人口有能力維持香港的長遠經濟和社會發展。」<br />\n<br />\n2007年，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>曾蔭權提出香港人口要突破1000萬的目標</strong></span>，又<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>提出香港人口老化問題嚴重。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他呼籲港人多生育，同時又提出放寬人口政策</strong></span>：香港一面鼓勵内地人移民香港（包括優才計劃和鼓勵在港陸生畢業留港），一面鼓勵雙非父母在香港生育，以補充香港人口的長遠不足。<br />\n<br />\n在回歸初期，中央大體上尊重香港政府，這些人口政策完全是香港自己的事，沒有中央施壓的成分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>貪曾禍港，罪在貪曾。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"882b088245d190c0ba5212dcad9970be1ee32294","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔係有無得傾，係敢唔敢傾"},{"pid":"cfc8de10145f7f02de798d97d465b9fed08abf50","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"882b088245d190c0ba5212dcad9970be1ee32294","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔係有無得傾，係敢唔敢傾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"想傾，香港自己本身要傾掂數先<br />\n<br />\n先搞掂左班左膠先啦<br />\n<br />\n之後仲有人口不足膠，人口老化膠先。<br />\n<br />\n一陣間再醒過1000萬人口目標，到時候每日200人甚至300人添。"},{"pid":"290af9445dcf568f1e1dcaafe6741b314554aead","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc8de10145f7f02de798d97d465b9fed08abf50","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"882b088245d190c0ba5212dcad9970be1ee32294","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔係有無得傾，係敢唔敢傾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"想傾，香港自己本身要傾掂數先<br />\n<br />\n先搞掂左班左膠先啦<br />\n<br />\n之後仲有人口不足膠，人口老化膠先。<br />\n<br />\n一陣間再醒過1000萬人口目標，到時候每日200人甚至300人添。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"咩都假，每日明正言順百幾廉價勞工輸入，張宇人之流最開心<br />\n人口不足/老化問題輸入一班咬老綜既有咩用，相反增加負擔"},{"pid":"b2b6f2314aec9c919f99c433c9e847b0df14e2a7","tid":712534,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"人大：我就係法律"},{"pid":"998f4568b31f5a91f341e9cb5d3a8d401e9b4b73","tid":712534,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"傾係有得傾 立法會過唔過又係另一件事"},{"pid":"aed2048666f2b9b4dd14f43a476be4aebebd3479","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"290af9445dcf568f1e1dcaafe6741b314554aead","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc8de10145f7f02de798d97d465b9fed08abf50","tid":712534,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"882b088245d190c0ba5212dcad9970be1ee32294","tid":712534,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔係有無得傾，係敢唔敢傾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"想傾，香港自己本身要傾掂數先<br />\n<br />\n先搞掂左班左膠先啦<br />\n<br />\n之後仲有人口不足膠，人口老化膠先。<br />\n<br />\n一陣間再醒過1000萬人口目標，到時候每日200人甚至300人添。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"咩都假，每日明正言順百幾廉價勞工輸入，張宇人之流最開心<br />\n人口不足/老化問題輸入一班咬老綜既有咩用，相反增加負擔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"輸入專才優才一樣死<br />\n<br />\n專才優才最叻係咩：搵錢，投資<br />\n<br />\n專才投資能力強，物價樓價一定暴升"},{"pid":"cb89fa07e5fe8f4a2499c0849b0894ca29268362